item.content:encoded:
Toy-Match is a matching-3 game. You can be relaxed in this game. The mission is to collect some directional things. It is easy, just match three or more same color blocks to a line. If you match the blocks with the background, it will collect them. When you collect all the props, you can continue the next level. But your moves are limited, you should better collect them before running out of moves. Sounds difficult? Do not be upset, we will mention you if you actually do not know how to move. Let us enjoy the game!
Click to play.

The cards matching in numerical order, but only the different colors can match. This makes the game harder. But I believe you can solve this card puzzle by […]
item.content:encoded:
One Cell is a solitaire card game. You can have fun in a poker game here. It is a little difficult, you have to match specific cards. The cards matching in numerical order, but only the different colors can match. This makes the game harder. But I believe you can solve this card puzzle by your wisdom. The Aces will be collected that can help you a little. Also, you can put a card to the free cell temporarily when you have no way to move the cards. Only you have three chances to undo the moves. If you can not figure out, only one thing you can do is restart.

item.content:encoded:
Truck Loader Online Master is a cartoon-style 2D game. Players need to drive the truck to move back and forth, transport the goods to the designated location, and then deliver the container to the truck. It is worth noting that some levels have only one container, and most There are many containers in the level of, so players need to make good use of the magnet function to attach the goods to the iron products, and finally place the containers on the truck. This game requires great patience, wish you success!
use arrow keys and click the mouse to play.

item.content:encoded:
Incremental Epic Breakers is an interesting new arcade game with digital graphics in different colors and many levels. After completing the challenge, you will get rewards for upgrading. Only the red ball, white ball, and bullet on the cannon can damage the monster. The logo on the upper left is the logo of the base. After completing the mission, you will get a lot of coins. Are you ready for the challenge?
Right-Click on a monster to try capture with a trap.
